name: Pregnant Violetta at Ambulance
description:
Pregnant Violetta at Ambulance is Game to learn how to take care Pregnant Lady During emergency in Ambulance.
Use Different Tools for Treatment like
- Thermometer to measure temperature
- Apply Injection
- Check Sonography to check Baby Health.
- Give her medicine to control Blood pressure.
- Apply Oxizen mask She is facing breathing problem
- If you Face any problem than press on hint.
